## Shortcut

Checkout the template presentation repo:
```sh
git clone https://github.com/theno/revealjs_template  ~/repos/my_presi
```

Then:
* Adjust `<title>reveal.js template</title>` in __`index.html`__
* Edit __`slides.md`__
